node-red-contrib-multiflexi (0.3.1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Fix per-entity palette icons not rendering: reference the icon
    module-prefixed ("node-red-contrib-multiflexi/<file>") so resolution does
    not depend on def.set (unreliable for types registered in the async catalog
    callback). node-red already serves the cached files; this makes the editor
    use them.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Sat, 14 Jun 2026 09:00:00 +0200

node-red-contrib-multiflexi (0.3.0) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Catalog icons now come from the MultiFlexi web image endpoints
    (appimage.php / companylogo.php / credentialimage.php) instead of base64
    in the push payload. New MULTIFLEXI_APP_URL node setting (default
    /multiflexi/); the catalog node fetches+caches each icon and the editor
    registers it client-side so the palette renders without a node-red restart.
  * Ship a writable module icon dir (symlink to /var/lib/node-red-contrib-
    multiflexi/icons) so per-entity icons can be cached on a read-only install.
  * Ship a systemd drop-in adding /usr/share/node-red to the node-red service
    NODE_PATH so node-red starts correctly.

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Fri, 12 Jun 2026 10:30:00 +0200

